values:
Lolololol 
Some kid was playing IWSNT loudly in the parking lot.
I haven't heard that in a while.
sometimes i can't help but think that i'm in a play.

i keep having day dreams where i have horrible panic attacks.
im worried that all of this 'getting fucked up' is breaking me down.
even though i feel this way, sadly i cant stop.

<lj-cut text="gunslinger extraordinaire">

today has been tiring
yet i didnt really do anything
i was just there.

i blame the mood on the weather
because no one likes to blame themselves.

english was surprisingly easy
but anything is when people do the work for you.

a 20 ounce pop and a vending machine snack
do not make for a good meal.
thankfully someone had my back.
a cold, smushed burger probably wasnt better
but it sure did hit the spot.


</lj-cut>
